THE QUANTUM FOAM · node FOM · FOM · THE QUANTUM FOAM · techne · spacetime, frothing · UD0 / techne

universe of origin : the art — a generative rendering of a scale
seal               : In the 1950s the physicist John Wheeler proposed that at very small scales, spacetime is not calm but turbulent — a 'quantum foam' of bubbles and wormhole-like loops blinking in and out of existence, driven by the same uncertainty that fills the vacuum with fleeting particles. It has never been observed. This sphere draws it: a froth that forms and pops, forever unsettled.
